<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #4f5ef1;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .message-sm {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        .message-sm > h1 {
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: white;
        }
        .message-sm > p {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 0;
            color: white;
        }
        .course-info {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .course-info > h4 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4f5ef1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        table th, table td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        table th {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 500;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        table td {
            color: #333;
        }
        .total-row {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #ddd;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .footer > p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-sm">
            <h1>Your Elearning Order is Confirmed!</h1>
            <p>We're just as excited as you are ðŸŽ‰</p>
        </div>
        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's What You Ordered</h4>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td><strong>Order #:</strong> <%= order._id %></td>
                    <td><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Item</th>
                        <th>Quantity</th>
                        <th>Cost</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><%= order.name %></td>
                        <td>1</td>
                        <td><%= order.price %>â‚«</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <div class="total-row">
                <p><strong>Subtotal:</strong> <%= order.price %>â‚«</p>
                <p><strong>Total:</strong> <%= order.price %>â‚«</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@elearning.com">support@elearning.com</a></p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Elearning. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>